tyle=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">телефон </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#5}Ота-онанинг телефон рақами</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">АРИЗА</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">(ўқувчини бир мактабдан бошқасига ўтказиш тўғрисида)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Менинг фарзандим </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Боланинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> бугунги кунда </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Мактаб сони</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-сон мактабда </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Бола ўқиётган синф реквизитлари</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> синфда ўқийди. </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Бошқа мактабга ўтказиш сабаблари</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">сабабли бошқа мактабга ўтказиш зарурати мавжуд.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Шунга кўра, фарзандим </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Боланинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">ни </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Бола ўтказилиши сўралаётган мактаб реквизитлари</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">мактабга ўтказишга рухсат беришингизни сўрайман.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Ариза ёзилган сана</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Имзо ўрни</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#4}Ота-онанинг Ф.И.О.си</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 348.69806094183px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
